    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>《暗星铁律》的全部净收入的 1% 将通过挪威难民理事会（Norwegian Refugee Council，NRC）捐赠，用于支持在冲突地区被迫逃离暴力的人们；NRC 是一个政治中立的人道主义组织，致力于援助因战争、流离失所和压迫而受到影响的平民。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/315fa3f0b0943b10848ab8f53d5e2246.avif?t=1770731515\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras_big/315fa3f0b0943b10848ab8f53d5e2246.webp?t=1770731515 width=1560 height=131 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《暗星铁律》邀请你在黑色讽刺风格的殖民模拟 + 类 Roguelite FPS混合游戏中，奠定史上最伟大政权的基石。作为领袖，管理公民、传播属于你的真理，并将此地从当前统治势力的压迫中解放。请务必明智地决策：你的抉择将使社会变得更好，或更坏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/86379efcb968e241b1844ab07dbd3c83.avif?t=1770731515\" width=1560 height=304 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/073077c648457d490a3fd1517c78da55.poster.avif?t=1770731515\" width=780 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/073077c648457d490a3fd1517c78da55.webm?t=1770731515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/073077c648457d490a3fd1517c78da55.mp4?t=1770731515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过实施暴虐或仁慈的统治来塑造你的民众，掌控他们的恐惧、幸福、饥饿与忠诚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用宣传、监控塔、鞭笞与公开处决来教化他们，直到他们在梦里也甘愿为国家奉献。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者以仁政的远见开启新时代，为曾经绝望的人们提供医疗关怀、舒适和繁荣的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每道法令，既决定着你的政权气质，也拿捏着芸芸众生的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/d2b157d6f7ef6af225b18d017d7e2905.avif?t=1770731515\" width=1560 height=304 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/1ef20d9b2f1f9d4977a0f941629b6511.poster.avif?t=1770731515\" width=780 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/1ef20d9b2f1f9d4977a0f941629b6511.webm?t=1770731515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/1ef20d9b2f1f9d4977a0f941629b6511.mp4?t=1770731515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建设国家机器。从最初的少数幸存者开始，打造出紧密运转、自给自足的集体机器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩张你的基地。将其从几间零散的庇护所升级为能够容纳快速增长人口的庞大综合体，每个公民都服务于你的宏图大计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >研究新科技、新建筑、新政策，提升殖民地效率，巩固你的统治。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规划、建造、自动化你的生产流水线并监视设施以冷酷而精准的工业节奏运转。每次升级都是效率的提高，每座建筑都是你愿景的注脚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/67c02039a55daa541c74f7de5499a08c.avif?t=1770731515\" width=1560 height=304 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/fb68b08012e40dea74d4f85adfb0f8c6.poster.avif?t=1770731515\" width=780 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/fb68b08012e40dea74d4f85adfb0f8c6.webm?t=1770731515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/fb68b08012e40dea74d4f85adfb0f8c6.mp4?t=1770731515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为基地领袖，你将深入泰瑞斯星系，征服被敌对政权割据的宇宙领土。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >征召新的公民，获取关键资源，与流动商人交易......你撼动已有结构的决策和行动，都会影响当地民众的状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将率军投入战场。从绝境中的小规模交火到包含步兵、坦克与机甲的大规模机械化战场，每次胜利都让你的政权影响力更加深远。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次征战，你尽可以在数百种 Roguelite 加成里自由选择，铸就通往至高战力的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每轮战役的收获都会壮大你的基地、你的军队，以及作为领袖的你：新资源、新士兵、以及解锁高阶职业技能的经验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你绝不会经历两次完全相同的征战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067360/extras/5f26925938b38a483950a367d167d1c2.avif?t=1770731515\" width=1560 height=304 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《暗星铁律》是一款融合了殖民地模拟与 Roguelite FPS 的作品，让基地建设、公民管理与第一人称战术作战共同发生在科幻反乌托邦的世界里。它提供易于上手的射击和平易近人的模拟体验，并在关键部分提供足够的深度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，你可以看见关于权力的一切：它如何建立，如何腐化，如何消耗和毁灭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你将指挥军队、颁布法律，在每一张对你充满敬意或畏惧的面孔上，见证你统治的结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>国家注视一切</u></strong> <br>历史将如何铭记你？</p>",
